# ⚡ PART 8: Common Errors & Fixes

## ❌ Permission Denied

```bash
chmod 600 key.pem
```

---

## ❌ Key Not Found

```bash
ssh -i /full/path/key.pem ubuntu@<ip>
```

---

## ❌ Wrong Username

* Ubuntu → ubuntu
* Amazon Linux → ec2-user

---

## ❌ Connection Timeout

* Check Security Group → Allow Port 22

